\centerline{\bf On the probability that two elements of a finite semigroup\footnote{National Research, Development and Innovation Office NKFIH, 115288 \\ Keywords: probability, equivalence relations, right regular representation of semigroups, congruences on semigroups, MSC: 60B99, 20M10 } }
\centerline{\bf have the same right matrix}
\bigskip
\centerline{Attila Nagy}
\centerline{\it Department of Algebra}
